  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Small bowel obstruction surgery is frequent and would benefit from enhanced recovery&#xD;
      programs. While some studies advocate for their feasibility, it has never been proved and&#xD;
      prospective studies are required to confirm the feasibility of such program and the impact on&#xD;
      postoperative outcomes.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
